WEBVTT

00:07.641 --> 00:08.542
‐ Previously on
"The Betty Broderick Story"...

00:09.309 --> 00:10.077
‐ Are you sleeping with her?

00:10.110 --> 00:11.411
‐ If this is where
your head goes

00:11.445 --> 00:14.915
when you don't get your way,
that's the real problem.

00:14.948 --> 00:16.917
You should get some
professional help for that.

00:16.950 --> 00:19.520
I can't prove
that something's not true.

00:19.553 --> 00:20.487
That it doesn't exist.

00:20.521 --> 00:22.856
I am not sleeping
with Linda Kolkena.

00:22.890 --> 00:24.091
‐ What are you doing?

00:24.124 --> 00:25.259
‐ If I don't take this time,

00:25.292 --> 00:27.361
I'm not going to be any good
to anyone.

00:27.394 --> 00:28.962
‐ He told you he was leaving?
‐ What did he say?

00:28.996 --> 00:31.331
‐ That he needed space
and time.

00:31.365 --> 00:32.199
I'm jealous.

00:32.232 --> 00:33.166
Who couldn't use a break
from everything?

00:33.200 --> 00:34.902
‐ What is this?
How long have you been here?

00:34.935 --> 00:36.336
‐ Since dark.

00:36.370 --> 00:37.371
‐ Yeah, she said you'd
be back eventually.

00:37.404 --> 00:40.774
‐ Dan's been granted temporary
physical custody.

00:40.807 --> 00:42.809
You need to be a good
soldier here, Bets.

00:42.843 --> 00:45.379
Otherwise you risk not being
able to see them at all.

00:45.412 --> 00:47.548
‐ Court order signed
by a judge.

00:47.581 --> 00:49.950
From now on, you come on
the Coral Reef property

00:49.983 --> 00:51.985
with my permission,
or you go to jail.

00:52.019 --> 00:53.220
‐ How am I supposed
to see my kids?

00:53.253 --> 00:54.388
‐ With my permission!

00:54.421 --> 00:57.958
‐ Everyone whose last name
is Broderick is gonna lose.

01:00.561 --> 01:03.463
‐ Christmas is always such
a big production for her.

01:03.497 --> 01:05.966
