30:31.830 --> 30:34.199
[eggs rattling]

30:38.437 --> 30:40.772
‐ Taking it in the chops
time after time,

30:40.806 --> 30:43.041
doing nothing
in self defense.

30:43.075 --> 30:44.543
You turn your hate inward.

30:44.576 --> 30:47.112
You hurt yourself even more.

30:47.145 --> 30:49.381
Nice girls slit their wrists
over the kitchen sink

30:49.414 --> 30:52.084
so they don't make a mess.

30:52.117 --> 30:54.886
How can anyone survive
under this kind of assault?

30:54.920 --> 30:57.089
